Public Function DeCode(Code As String)

    For xy = 1 To Len(Code)
        Ascii = Asc(Mid(Code, xy, 1))
        Change = Ascii - 29
        NewCode = NewCode & Chr(Change)
    Next
    
    DeCode = NewCode & vbCr

End Function
